Description: Tab system and system statistics for your terminal. 
 MyScreen  is  a program that runs GNU/Screen with a tab system and system sta‚Äê
 tistics provided by myscreen-stats.   It  is  expected  to  consume  very  few
 resources.
 .
 MyScreen  includes GNU/Screen configuration file and myscreen-stats, a program
 that provides several statistics.  The configuration file of GNU/Screen allows
 to enable hardstatus bar in the manner of a tab system of graphical terminals.
 The  program  myscreen-stats  provides several informations like the number of
 users connected, the uptime, the upload and download rates, the battery state,
 the  wifi  quality, the loadaverage, the number of processes , the cpus rates,
 the disks rates, the ram and swap percentages.
